description:
Join us for our second project fair of the 2018-2019 school year, it is open to everyone. Project Fair is the main event for project leads and teams to recruit members, so be sure to see what's up and see how you can get hands-on!

We current have three amazing projects, two of which involve a drone and the third is an iOS app. We are also looking for some more projects to add to our organization so if you have an idea, we highly encourage you to fill out our project application here: https://goo.gl/forms/TBIxjCuQ4twK8lz72

If you are planning on attending this event please click "Going".
Food will be provided!

If you have any questions please feel free to message us or send us an email at div-e@ucsd.edu
You can also learn more about our projects on our website:
div-e.ucsd.edu
name: DivE Project Fair 2019
